                      <span>10</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2000-06-21</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I bought this book in the early 80's and absolutely loved it. I recommended it to friends who were going to spend a year in Russia. They took it with them and shared it with their Russian friends, who copied whole chapters by hand -- all the while bemoaning the loss of so much of their rich, pre-revolutionary culture.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">AN ABSOLUTE TREASURE</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
